  "detailed_description": "A father, a son and their faith in a myth. Bloomyth is a puzzle and adventure video game in which you will enter the search for the last hope to save a life. Explore and stay alert along the way, overcome obstacles, solve puzzles and... Watch out for time, there is no turning back!.<br><br>-Find out the truth behind the Bloomyth<br>-Overcome the obstacles correctly to reach the temple on time<br>-Enjoy the relaxing theme<br>-Focus and solve the puzzles<br>-Get both endings of the game<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2832730/extras/326c16115f5a1635a5b892ca12da6763.avif?t=1709272975\" width=300 height=300 /></span>",
